{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first was the-- the nonsense-- all the walls, all the defiance we saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, Nazi slogans and graffiti on all the walls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then they all gave up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We call it being snow blind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we roll into a town, it'd be fluttering with bed sheets, pillowcases, handkerchiefs, anything white they could get out would be fluttering out the window.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they gave up fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The first thing we learned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The second thing we learned is-- of course, we were advance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were-- we'd go through fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Infantry might take a day or two to catch up with us, so there's a gap in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what the Germans themselves were terrified of was their own SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they'd come out of the woods and kill any Germans that hung out a white flag, if the Americans had gone on ahead, or they'd left a little vacuum in the rear.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Germans would say to me, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The SS, they're not human anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were terrified of themselves that they-- the SS were criminals, no question about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the German civilians were as afraid of as anybody else was, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember in the city of Speyer on the Rhine, helping-- there were a crowd of German civilians huddled across the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had an aid station in a Gasthaus, an inn, and we're running ambulances up and down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was very heavy fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was one young German soldier had a leg badly torn up, and there were steps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I took his arm, got him over my shoulder, and helped-- carried him down the steps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And all the Germans were astounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They go, look, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He's helping a German, he's helping a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
